Package: ntc
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Navigate, Tree, Cat - A combined directory tree viewer and file concatenator
 ntc is a CLI tool for navigating directories, viewing file trees,
 and concatenating file contents with a rich interactive shell.
 It features fuzzy search, backup/restore with SHA256 integrity,
 teleport bookmarks, custom aliases, file watching, and multiple
 report formats (TXT, JSON, Markdown, HTML, PDF, DOCX, XLSX).
